<section class="Sh">
<h1 class="Sh" id="EXAMPLES"><a class="permalink" href="#EXAMPLES">EXAMPLES</a></h1>
This shows all PCI devices on the system:
<p class="Pp"></p>
<div class="Bd Bd-indent"><code class="Li">pcictl pci0 list</code></div>
<p class="Pp">This shows all PCI devices on the system, including attached
    drivers:</p>
<p class="Pp"></p>
<div class="Bd Bd-indent"><code class="Li">pcictl pci0 list -N</code></div>
</section>
